&lt;li&gt;Edit and refine content produced by other contributors, applying a consistent brand and editorial voice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI-assisted tools to accelerate drafting, research, and iteration — and know when to rely on craft over automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex financial and product concepts into clear, accessible language for a broad consumer audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the compliance process for Product Education content — submitting assets, managing redlines, tracking approvals, and executing required changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clear, up-to-date compliance tracker so the team always knows where each asset stands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively follow up with compliance stakeholders to keep reviews moving and timelines intact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Management &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
