&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience with credit data and credit processes, or a related financial services role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of working directly with credit reporting agencies (Experian, TransUnion, Equifax) and/or third-party credit data companies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of credit data flows, operational data processes and standards&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
